{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Meeting_with_Fate",
  "title": "A Meeting with Fate",
  "summary": "In the Bonadan spaceport, the Jedi Jessalyn searches the ship berths with her companions Altair and Blaze for a particular vessel. A dark-haired stranger named Clarise approaches and, claiming to be a fortune-teller who once read Jessalyn's cards in the presence of Luke Skywalker, lures her away with the promise of a New Republic pin supposedly given to her by Luke himself. Following Clarise into a droid-run mechanized factory, Jessalyn is ambushed when the woman ignites a lightsaber and reveals herself as a servant of the dark side. A long, brutal duel rages across the factory's catwalks, conveyors, and production lines, both women hurling debris and Force attacks, until Jessalyn's leg is broken and her weapon lost. Clarise finally overpowers her, slams her head against the floor, and -- invoking the name of Lord Valak, whose lightsaber she wields -- leaves Jessalyn unconscious and broken, wrapping her in her own Jedi robes to carry her off as a captive.",
